{"tid":2309444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立陶宛政府向受政權迫害的白羅斯人免費發放立陶宛國家簽證","createTime":"2020-12-02T14:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:14:41.000Z","uid":310867,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f78d03c5a55aa3c92e742c3cb54f2eb894d173cf","tid":2309444,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tsihanouskaya/status/1334121916123262977?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftsihanouskaya%2Fstatus%2F1334121916123262977%3Fs%3D21&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=3662eff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftsihanouskaya%2Fstatus%2F1334121916123262977%3Fs%3D21&h=c68b0319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tsihanouskaya/status/1334121916123262977?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nOn 2 December, the Government has decided to issue Lithuanian national visas free of charge to regime-persecuted Belarusians. The proposal was brought forward by the Ministry of Foreign Affairs.<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Repressions and violence against Belarusian citizens and gross human rights violations have led to an increasing number of those seeking asylum and temporary protection in Lithuania. To come and stay in Lithuania for a longer period, <span class=\"red\">Belarusian citizens must hold a long-term national visa, which has been charged 60 euros, until now. From now on, it will be free&rsquo;, </span>said Saulius Skvernelis, Acting Prime Minister.<br />\n本身收60歐元，而家免費<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lrv.lt/en/news/free-lithuanian-national-visas-for-regime-persecuted-belarusians\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flrv.lt%2Fen%2Fnews%2Ffree-lithuanian-national-visas-for-regime-persecuted-belarusians&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=81b55458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lrv.lt/en/news/free-lithuanian-national-visas-for-regime-persecuted-belarusians</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hannaliubakova/status/1334097705077977089?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannaliubakova%2Fstatus%2F1334097705077977089%3Fs%3D21&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d60d1774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannaliubakova%2Fstatus%2F1334097705077977089%3Fs%3D21&h=78d35b21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hannaliubakova/status/1334097705077977089?s=21</a><br />\n至今有10,000個白羅斯人離開至波蘭、3000個去咗烏克蘭、去立陶宛和拉脫維亞有500人"},{"pid":"fd62472cff9a875eccf3550804c2db6ec2e6677d","tid":2309444,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc37143ba03c5f114d68dd3e9e2089ba085bb6b","tid":2309444,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"根本有部分白羅斯領土係屬於立陶宛"},{"pid":"beffeb0d38590efe8d5ee49e4c9768a30c1ed88b","tid":2309444,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:20:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a397a4d2cead13e00f7b9577e6193c7499edaaf","tid":2309444,"uid":103374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"今明兩年將會係人類大遷徙<br />\n過多幾年全世界分開自由同獨裁兩個陣營"},{"pid":"2121ddeb1b1dd7c8c93469f358a52477d2b616ad","tid":2309444,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e94b99d2c09a8b2f993d9edeac1f7ac43bb682","tid":2309444,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif